ight: 200px; display: none;"><img src="https://res.public.onecdn.static.microsoft/officeonline/hashed/79b48a07e8b20228/spiral.gif" class="loading" style="top: calc(50% + 20px);"></div><div id="pc1"><div style="height: 0px;"></div><div class="pageNumV2">1 / 1</div><div id="p1" name="p1"><div style="overflow-y: auto; direction: ltr;"><div style="display: inline-block;"><table border="1" style="direction:ltr"><tbody><tr><td><div style="direction:ltr;margin-top:5px"><span style="direction:ltr;">Employee Name: &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <br></span></div></td><td><div style="direction:ltr;margin-top:5px"><span style="direction:ltr;">Date: &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<br></span></div></td></tr><tr><td><div style="direction:ltr;margin-top:5px"><span style="direction:ltr;">Employee #: &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <br></span></div></td><td><div style="direction:ltr;margin-top:5px"><span style="direction:ltr;">Location #: &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<br></span></div></td></tr><tr><td><div style="direction:ltr;margin-top:5px"><span style="direction:ltr;">Hire Date: &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <br></span></div></td><td><div style="direction:ltr;margin-top:5px"><span style="direction:ltr;">Department: &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <br></span></div></td></tr><tr><td><div style="direction:ltr;margin-top:5px"><span style="direction:ltr;">Current Position: &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <br></span></div></td><td><div style="direction:ltr;margin-top:5px"><span style="direction:ltr;"> &nbsp;<br></span></div></td></tr></tbody></table></div></div><div style="direction:ltr;margin-top:5px"><span style="direction:ltr;"> <br></span></div><div style="direction:ltr;margin-top:5px"><b><span style="direction:ltr;">SMART Goals</span></b><span style="direction:ltr;"> <br></span></div><div style="direction:ltr;margin-top:5px"><b><span style="direction:ltr;">Specific </span></b><span style="direction:ltr;">ŌĆō<b><span style="direction:ltr;"> </span></b><span style="direction:ltr;">Is straightforward and states what you want to happen, with a clearly defined objective or direction <br></span></span></div><div style="direction:ltr;margin-top:5px"><b><span style="direction:ltr;">Measurable </span></b><span style="direction:ltr;">ŌĆō<b><span style="direction:ltr;"> </span></b><span style="direction:ltr;">Has a quantity, quality, cost, or action associated with the goal &nbsp;<br></span></span></div><div style="direction:ltr;margin-top:5px"><b><span style="direction:ltr;">Achievable </span></b><span style="direction:ltr;">ŌĆō Is high enough to be a challenge, but not so high that itŌĆÖs unreachable <br></span></div><div style="direction:ltr;margin-top:5px"><b><span style="direction:ltr;">Results oriented </span></b><span style="direction:ltr;">ŌĆō Is consistent with your other goals and makes a difference to the needs of your department and of <span style="direction:ltr;">Costco &nbsp;<br></span></span></div><div style="direction:ltr;margin-top:5px"><b><span style="direction:ltr;">Time-bound </span></b><span style="direction:ltr;">ŌĆō Specific period of time with start and end dates to give you a clear target to work towards <br></span></div><div style="direction:ltr;margin-top:5px"><span style="direction:ltr;"> <br></span></div><div style="direction:ltr;margin-top:5px"><span style="direction:ltr;">After each goal, explain what the benefit of completing the goal will be to the employee and/or the business. <br></span></div><div style="direction:ltr;margin-top:5px"><span style="direction:ltr;"> <br></span></div><div style="direction:ltr;margin-top:5px"><i><span style="direction:ltr;">Example: </span></i><span style="direction:ltr;"> <br></span></div><div style="direction:ltr;margin-top:5px"><i><span style="direction:ltr;">With every member, provide exceptional member service by following CostcoŌĆÖs member service expectations* and follow-up with my </span></i><i><span style="direction:ltr;">manager weekly to receive feedback. &nbsp;*Eye contact, smile, greet and acknowledge each member sincerely, appreciate and thank </span></i><i><span style="direction:ltr;">every member, be accountable and take responsibility. &nbsp;</span></i><span style="direction:ltr;"> <br></span></div><div style="direction:ltr;margin-top:5px"><span style="direction:ltr;"> <br></span></div><div style="direction:ltr;margin-top:5px"><i><span style="direction:ltr;">Benefit: &nbsp;Show improvement on my performance review (member service category), which will help me when I apply for different job </span></i><i><span style="direction:ltr;">postings. &nbsp;Plus, it will make the day-to-day experience of the members who come through my line more enjoyable. </span></i><span style="direction:ltr;"> <br></span></div><div style="direction:ltr;margin-top:5px"><span style="direction:ltr;"> <br></span></div><div style="direction:ltr;margin-top:5px"><b><span style="direction:ltr;">3 to 5 SMART Goals ŌĆō Suggested in advance by the employee; finalized with the Manager.</span></b><span style="direction:ltr;"> <br></span></div><div style="direction:ltr;margin-top:5px"><span style="direction:ltr;"> <br></span></div><div style="overflow-y: auto; direction: ltr;"><div style="display: inline-block;"><table border="1" style="direction:ltr"><tbody><tr><td><div style="direction:ltr;margin-top:5px"><b><i><span style="direction:ltr;">Employee-Suggested SMART Goals</span></i></b><span style="direction:ltr;"> <br></span></div></td><td><div style="direction:ltr;margin-top:5px"><b><i><span style="direction:ltr;">Final SMART Goals</span></i></b><span style="direction:ltr;"> <br></span></div></td></tr><tr><td><div style="direction:ltr;margin-top:5px"><span style="direction:ltr;"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<br></span></div></td><td><div style="direction:ltr;margin-top:5px"><span style="direction:ltr;"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<br></span></div></td></tr><tr><td><div style="direction:ltr;margin-top:5px"><span style="direction:ltr;"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<br></span></div></td><td><div style="direction:ltr;margin-top:5px"><span style="direction:ltr;"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<br></span></div></td></tr><tr><td><div style="direction:ltr;margin-top:5px"><span style="direction:ltr;"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<br></span></div></td><td><div style="direction:ltr;margin-top:5px"><span style="direction:ltr;"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<br></span></div></td></tr><tr><td><div style="direction:ltr;margin-top:5px"><span style="direction:ltr;"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<br></span></div></td><td><div style="direction:ltr;margin-top:5px"><span style="direction:ltr;"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<br></span></div></td></tr><tr><td><div style="direction:ltr;margin-top:5px"><span style="direction:ltr;"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<br></span></div></td><td><div style="direction:ltr;margin-top:5px"><span style="direction:ltr;"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<br></span></div></td></tr></tbody></table></div></div><div style="direction:ltr;margin-top:5px"><span style="direction:ltr;"> <br></span></div><div style="direction:ltr;margin-top:5px"><span style="direction:ltr;"> <br></span></div><div style="direction:ltr;margin-top:5px"><span style="direction:ltr;"> <br></span></div><div style="direction:ltr;margin-top:5px"><span style="direction:ltr;">________________________________ &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;________________________________ &nbsp;<br></span></div><div style="direction:ltr;margin-top:5px"><span style="direction:ltr;">EmployeeŌĆÖs Signature &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;ManagerŌĆÖs Signature <br></span></div><div style="direction:ltr;margin-top:5px"><span style="direction:ltr;"> &nbsp; &nbsp; <br></span></div></div><hr class="pageHrV2"></div><div id="m_endBuffer" style="height: 200px; display: none;"><img src="https://res.public.onecdn.static.microsoft/officeonline/hashed/79b48a07e8b20228/spiral.gif" class="loading"></div></div></div></div><div id="m_loadingLayer" class="layer" style="z-index: 1; visibility: visible; display: none;"><img src="https://res